videos.headline: South Carolina takes early lead after Nick Muse easily scores TD
videos.description: Luke Doty finds an open Nick Muse for the easy 2-yard touchdown catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (South Carolina takes early lead after Nick Muse easily scores TD) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jaheim Bell shows off jets on 82-yard TD
videos.description: South Carolina gets the explosive play as Jaheim Bell hauls in the pass and goes right by the Vanderbilt defense for an 82-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jaheim Bell shows off jets on 82-yard TD) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan Strachan tips INT to himself
videos.description: South Carolina edge rusher Jordan Strachan tips the ball into the air and picks it off, then returns it into Vanderbilt territory.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jordan Strachan tips INT to himself) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vanderbilt capitalizes on fumble with TD
videos.description: Vanderbilt gets the ball in South Carolina territory after they recover a fumble. A few plays later Rocko Griffin punches it in from 1-yard out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Vanderbilt capitalizes on fumble with TD) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sheppard breaks tackle and takes off for 52-yard Vandy TD
videos.description: Vanderbilt takes the lead after Will Sheppard hauls in the short pass, breaks a tackle and takes off down the sideline for a 52-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sheppard breaks tackle and takes off for 52-yard Vandy TD) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Doty airmails receiver, results in Vandy INT
videos.description: Luke Doty throws it over his receiver's head and it's picked off by Vanderbilt's Dashaun Jerkins.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Doty airmails receiver, results in Vandy INT) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: South Carolina takes the lead with under a minute left
videos.description: Zeb Noland rips a pass to the back of the end zone to Xavier Legette for the touchdown and the lead with under a minute remaining in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (South Carolina takes the lead with under a minute left) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: South Carolina clinches win with sack-fumble
videos.description: Vanderbilt quarterback Mike Wright is stripped and South Carolina recovers, clinching the one-point win.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (South Carolina clinches win with sack-fumble) 2021/10/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: South Carolina takes down Vanderbilt in back-and-forth affair
videos.description: South Carolina overcomes fourth quarter mistakes to take down Vanderbilt 21-20.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (South Carolina takes down Vanderbilt in back-and-forth affair) 2021/10/16 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Nolan comes off bench, leads Gamecocks past Vanderbilt
videos.description: South Carolina QB Zeb Noland steps in on the final drive and connects with Xavier Legette to secure a 21-20 come-from-behind win over Vandy.

videos.headline: Beamer says 'we made it as ugly as we possibly could'
videos.description: South Carolina's Shane Beamer expresses how proud he is of his Gamecocks and their resilience to keep fighting to the end against the Commodores.
